entry.title: Hydrologic Outlook issued May 08 at 2:54AM MDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Heavy rain mid to late week may lead to flooding... A strong storm system is expected to bring heavy rainfall to the area, starting Wednesday afternoon and continuing through Friday. Rainfall totals of 1 to 2 inches are likely through the event, with some pockets of 3+ inches possible. This heavy rain will cause rivers and streams to rise aggressively, with flooding possible
